Source: pmacasyn 
Section: devel
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Daron Chabot <dchabot@bnl.gov>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~), 
	       epics-dev (>= 3.14.11-2),
	       epics-synapps-dev (>= 20110728-2~lenny1)
Standards-Version: 3.8.4
Homepage: http://www.gmca.aps.anl.gov/TPMAC2/

Package: libpmacasynipport
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Libraries for working with Delta Tau Turbo PMACs within EPICS.
 This library contains the low-level PMAC communication support.
 .
 This package provides shared libraries.

Package: epics-pmacasynipport-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, 
	 libpmacasynipport (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Libraries for working with Delta Tau Turbo PMACs within EPICS.
 This library contains the low-level PMAC communication support.
 .
 This package contains files which may be used to run IOCs using
 the synApps Motor Record and pmacasynmotor.

Package: libpmacasynmotor
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, 
	 libpmacasynipport (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Libraries for working with Delta Tau Turbo PMACs within EPICS.
 This library contains the Motor Record device support.
 .
 This package provides shared libraries.

Package: epics-pmacasynmotor-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, 
	 epics-pmacasynipport-dev (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Libraries for working with Delta Tau Turbo PMACs within EPICS.
 This library contains the Motor Record device support.
 .
 This package contains files which may be used to run IOCs using
 the synApps Motor Record and pmacasynmotor.

Package: libpmacasyncoord
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, 
	 libpmacasynipport (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Libraries for working with Delta Tau Turbo PMACs within EPICS.
 This library contains support for mapping PMAC coordinate systems onto
 Motor Records.
 .
 This package provides shared libraries.

Package: epics-pmacasyncoord-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, 
	 epics-pmacasynipport-dev (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Libraries for working with Delta Tau Turbo PMACs within EPICS.
 This library contains support for mapping PMAC coordinate systems onto
 Motor Records.
 .
 This package contains files which may be used to run IOCs using
 the synApps Motor Record.
